* Inventor of Open Firmware and chairman of the IEEE Open Firmware Working Group
* Author of Forthmacs, SunForth, ForthMon, CForth83, OpenBoot, and (the FirmWorks implementation of) Open Firmware
* Vice Chairman of ANS Forth Technical Committee and author of many of the ANS Forth extension wordsets
* Firmware lead for the One Laptop Per Child "XO-1" laptop (which has Forth / Open Firmware as its boot ROM).
